{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Group"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Transaction\/TransactionModifier.swift#L84","fileName":"TransactionModifier.swift"},"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"transaction(_:)","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"name":"iOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"introducedAt":"10.15","unavailable":false,"name":"macOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"introducedAt":"6.0","unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE11transactionyQryAA11TransactionVzcF::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore5GroupV","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"((","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/group\/transaction(_:)"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Applies the given transaction mutation function to all animations used"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within the view."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Group\/transaction(_:)"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"transform"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","text":"Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"transform","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The transformation to apply to transactions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within this view."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all transactions used within the view."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Consider three identical animations controlled by a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"button that executes all three animations simultaneously:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The first animation rotates the “Rotation” "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view by 360"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"degrees."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The second uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to change the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“Rotation\\nModified” "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text"},{"type":"text","text":" view animation by a factor of 2."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third animation uses the "},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"replace the rotation animation affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view with a spring animation."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The following code implements these animations:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State private var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation =","                            view.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation = .interactiveSpring(","                            response: 0.60,","                            dampingFraction: 0.20,","                            blendDuration: 0.25)","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    self.flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier on leaf views such as ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Image","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" rather","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"than container views such as ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HStack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":". The","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transformation applies to all child views within this view; calling"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" on a container view can lead to unbounded scope of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"execution depending on the depth of the view hierarchy."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/View":{"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"View","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"View","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that represents part of your app’s user interface and provides"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"modifiers that you use to configure views."}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/view","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","role":"symbol"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Transaction":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Transaction","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Transaction","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/transaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","abstract":[{"text":"The context of the current state-processing update.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Button":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Button","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Button","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/button","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"